  <span id="freeText2189455283086653543" style="display:none"><b>William Styron's <i>The Confessions of Nat Turner</i></b><br><br><b>THE GATHERING</b><br><br>Whereupon all members of the congregation are seated.<br><br><b>THE LECTIONARY</b><br><br><b>First Reading</b><br><br><blockquote>
